Harry McCoy https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harry_McCoy 0 Harry McCoy (December 10, 1889 – September 1, 1937) was an American film actor and screenwriter. He appeared in 155 films between 1912 and 1935. He was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania, and died in Hollywood, California from a heart attack.
